icon_border_radius="500" icon_border_spacing="50"]Enable different Button animation effects on hover.[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type="selector" icon="dfd-icon-fencing" icon_color="#d8d8d8" icon_style="none" icon_color_bg="#ffffff" icon_color_border="#333333" icon_border_size="1" icon_border_radius="500" icon_border_spacing="50"]You may even add image as a Button background.[/ultimate_icon_list_item][ultimate_icon_list_item icon_type="selector" icon="dfd-icon-speedometer" icon_color="#d8d8d8" icon_style="none" icon_color_bg="#ffffff" item.content:encoded: Stainless steel, shagreen leather and flax fabric underline both the high status and the ability to be satisfied with simple things. This chair will suit perfectly the interiors in minimalist style and creative dwellings.
item.excerpt:encoded: Amazing combination of steel, leather and fabric underlines the reserved Scandinavian style.
